org.apache.beam.runners.dataflow

Interface TransformTranslator<TransformT extends PTransform>


  • @Internal
public interface TransformTranslator<TransformT extends PTransform>
    A TransformTranslator knows how to translate a particular subclass of PTransform for the Cloud Dataflow service. It does so by mutating the TransformTranslator.TranslationContext.
